## Position and Duration
- Position: AI Intern  
- Duration: 3 months  
- Start Date: [Start Date]

## Stipend
- Stipend: INR 10,000 per month (this is referred to as "stipend", not "salary").

## Work Location
- Work location: Fully remote. Candidate is located in Bengaluru.

## Type of Engagement
- This is an internship / temporary engagement. The intern has no entitlement to employee benefits (such as health insurance, paid leave, retirement benefits, etc.) unless explicitly stated in writing by Omninuera.

## Expected Commitment
- Expected weekly commitment: 20â€“40 hours per week (suggested). Working hours are flexible to accommodate remote work and mutually agreed schedules.

## Reporting
- You will report to: [Reporting Manager].

## Key Responsibilities
As an AI Intern, your responsibilities will include but are not limited to:
- Data preparation and cleaning for machine learning workflows.
- Designing and running model experiments.
- Evaluating model performance and producing analysis.
- Documenting methodologies, results, and reproducible workflows.
- Collaborating with the team on project tasks and knowledge sharing.

## Confidentiality and Intellectual Property
- You acknowledge that, in the course of your internship, you may have access to confidential information of Omninuera and its partners. You agree to maintain the confidentiality of such information during and after the internship.
- All intellectual property, inventions, discoveries, developments, ideas, improvements, trade secrets, and works of authorship (including but not limited to code, models, datasets, documentation, and designs) that you conceive, create, develop, or reduce to practice, either solely or jointly with others, during the period of your internship and related to Omninuera's business or projects, are the exclusive property of Omninuera. You hereby assign (or agree to assign) to Omninuera all right, title, and interest in and to such intellectual property and agree to execute any documents reasonably requested by Omninuera to perfect its rights.

## Termination / Early Exit
- Either party may terminate this internship with one (1) week written notice to the other party.
- Omninuera may terminate the internship immediately for cause, including but not limited to breach of confidentiality, misconduct, material non-performance, or illegal activity.

## Stipend Payment Schedule
- The stipend will be paid monthly via bank transfer.
- Please provide bank account details for stipend payment: [Bank Account Details for Stipend].

## Conditions
- This offer is subject to successful completion of any required background verification (if applicable) and legal/compliance review by Omninuera.
